{
    "pages": [
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "About what are they asking one another"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "About the momentous news"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "about which they differ"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "No indeed; they will come to know"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "Again no; they will come to know"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "Have We not made the earth a resting place"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "And the mountains as stakes"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "and created you in pairs"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "and made your sleep for rest"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "and made the night a covering"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "and made the day for seeking livelihood"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "and built above you seven mighty heavens"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "and made therein a blazing lamp"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "and sent down from the rainclouds abundant water"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "so that We may produce thereby grains and vegetation"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "and gardens with dense foliage"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "Indeed, the Day of Judgment is a time appointed"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "the Day when the Trumpet will be blown, you will come forth in crowds"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "and the sky will be opened up and will become gateways"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 20,
            "text": "and the mountains will vanish, becoming like a mirage"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 21,
            "text": "Indeed, Hell is lying in wait"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 22,
            "text": "a resort for the transgressors"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 23,
            "text": "wherein they will abide for endless ages"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 24,
            "text": "They will neither taste therein any coolness nor any drink"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 25,
            "text": "except scalding water and discharge of wounds"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 26,
            "text": "a fitting recompense"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 27,
            "text": "Indeed, they did not expect a reckoning"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 28,
            "text": "and utterly rejected Our verses"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 29,
            "text": "But We have enumerated everything in a record"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 30,
            "text": "So taste [the punishment], for We will not increase you except in torment.‚Äù"
        }
    ]
